          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", Cuomo has insisted that he fears that the tax initiative will prompt the super-rich to leave the state. On Wednesday, he doubled down, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
